isappearance in 1978 and return in 1986, and it‚Äôs perfect for unpacking why this movie is so interesting, educational, spiritually uplifting, and generation-defining, especially since you saw it in fragments at five. Let‚Äôs zoom in on that shift, weaving in your teleological causation idea, based on the teasers, box art, and partial TV viewing.</p>
